Re: Workplace-contact cease demand under 15 U.S.C. §1692c(a)(3)
Collector: {{ collection.collector_name or "the collection agency" }}

To whom it may concern,

This letter is written notice under the Fair Debt Collection Practices
Act, 15 U.S.C. §1692c(a)(3), that my employer prohibits collection
calls at my place of employment. You are not to contact me by phone,
